==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
Pinyin: jiāyóu (jia1 you2)
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: ka-iû
===[[Cantonese]]===
Yale: 

===Etymology===
From [[加]] ("add to," "increase," "augment") + [[油]] ("oil")

===Verb===
'''[[加]][[油]]''' (traditional and simplified)
# to oil; to lubricate;
#: ''[[这]][[台]][[机器]][[该]]'''加油'''[[了]]''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[這]][[台]][[機器]][[該]]'''加油'''[[了]]''
#: ''This machine needs '''oiling'''.''
# to refuel; to add gas
#: ''[[汽车]][[不用]]'''加油'''[[了]]''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[汽車]][[不用]]'''加油'''[[了]]''
#: ''No need to '''add gas''' to the car''
#: ''[[给]][[飞机]]'''加'''[[完]]'''油'''[[就]][[起飞]]''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[給]][[飛機]]'''加'''[[完]]'''油'''[[就]][[起飛]]''
#: ''Once the airplane is '''refueled''', we will take off''
# to make an extra effort
#: '' [[为了]][[早日]][[投产]]，[[从]][[厂长]][[到]][[工人]][[都]][[在]]'''加油'''[[干]]''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[為了]][[早日]][[投產]]，[[從]][[廠長]][[到]][[工人]][[都]][[在]]'''加油'''[[干]]''
#: ''In order to go into operation sooner, everyone, from the factory director down to the regular workers, is '''making an extra effort'''''.
#: '' [[活儿]][[剩下]][[不]][[多]][[了]]，[[大家]][[再]]'''加'''[[把]]'''油'''''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[活兒]][[剩下]][[不]][[多]][[了]]，[[大家]][[再]]'''加'''[[把]]'''油'''''
#: ''There's not much work left, let's everybody '''make an extra effort'''''.
# to cheer (player) on; go ...
#: ''[[观众]][[们]][[给]][[运动员]][[鼓掌]]'''加油'''''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[觀眾]][[們]][[給]][[運動員]][[鼓掌]]'''加油'''''
#: ''The crowd clapped and '''cheered on''' the athletes''
#: ''[[中国]][[队]]，'''加油'''！''&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;''[[中國]][[隊]]，'''加油'''﹗''
#: ''Go, team China!''

